Node "PartyGear"
notes "Put away weapon and armor are only visible if Connor has the respective items equipped."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "What do you want to know?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Can you use any weapons, Connor?" linkto "PartyWeapons"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Put away your weapon." linkto "PartyWeaponOff"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Take off the armor you're wearing." linkto "PartyArmorOff"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Actually, never mind. Something else I wanted to talk to you about..." linkto "Party"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PartyWeapons"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Ummm, I suppose I could use a knife if I had to. I fired a rifle once as well, and I suppose a shotgun's not that much different. Why do you ask though? We're not going somewhere dangerous are we?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Ah - no, Connor. Just making conversation. Something else I wanted to talk to you about..." linkto "Party"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let's move on, huh?" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PartyWeaponOff"
notes "Heal node only available if Connor is hurt"
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "It's probably for the best. I never felt all that comfortable around weapons."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you some questions." linkto "PartyQuestions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Heal yourself up, Connor." linkto "PartyHeal"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "We need to change our distance from each other." linkto "PartyDistance"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I need to talk to you about your gear." linkto "PartyGear"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait here until I come back." linkto "PartyWait"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay, let's go." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "PartyArmorOff"
notes "Heal node only available if Connor is hurt"
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well, okay. I'd feel safer with it on, though."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let me ask you some questions." linkto "PartyQuestions"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Heal yourself up, Connor." linkto "PartyHeal"  notes ""
