Node "PartyGAI"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Well, I can't say that I've heard of it. I'll keep an eye out for anything unusual around Sandover, though. Sorry I can't be more helpful."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "That's all right, Connor. I need to talk to you about something else." linkto "Party"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No problem. Let's move on." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Waiting"
notes "1) needs to check if maximum party has been exceeded, and link to node TooMany, or LowChr if the player's charisma prevents any party members. Otherwise, add Connor to the party."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Listen, I've been thinking - whatever made you ditch me before, I'm really sorry. Can you give me another chance?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sure thing, Connor. Let's get going." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hang tight a little while longer. I'll be back." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll give you another couple of weeks to think about what you did. Later." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "TooMany"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I'd love to come along - but I don't do well in large groups. I'd be happy to travel with a couple fewer people, though."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fine." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "LowChr"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[He looks closely at you.] Actually, I - I'm not sure that I really want to travel at the moment. Nothing personal, yeah?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Fine." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Talk"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Um, hello. Can I help you?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "What's your story?" linkto "Dubious"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "No, I'm just looking around. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You no happy? Me help?" linkto "Stoopid"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Dubious"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[He glances up warily.] Me? You want to know about me?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I asked, didn't I? Talk to me." linkto "Lifestory1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "On second thoughts, no. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Friends"
notes "1) Needs to link to a procedure that check's Fran's health and links appropriately to FranIll, FranDead or FranCured"
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "Oh, hello... You're back, how are you?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Not bad. How's your mother?" linkto "FranIll"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Good, thanks. I'll see you around." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "FranIll"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "She's very sick in the hospital. Doc Oswald's doing all he can for her at the moment. He's a good man, he'll do his best... but I just know it's hopeless."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "It sounds like there's not much you can do. Listen, I'm leaving here pretty soon. Why don't you come along with me?" linkto "JoinRefuseIll"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sorry to hear that, Connor. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "FranCured"
notes "1) needs to check if maximum party has been exceeded, and link to node TooMany, or LowChr if the player's charisma prevents any party members. Otherwise, add Connor to the party and go to JoinCured."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "She's doing great! Doctor Oswald told me that it's you who cured her. I owe you a huge debt, and if there's anything I can do to help you out, just ask."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How about you come along with me? It'll get you out of here, and I'm sure you can help me out." linkto "JoinCured"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'll bear it in mind. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "FranDead"
notes "1) needs to check if maximum party has been exceeded, and link to node TooMany, or LowChr if the player's charisma prevents any party members. Otherwise, add Connor to the party and go to JoinDead."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[He looks distraught.] She... she's dead. Alexander recently allowed euthanasia to be practiced in Sandover, and... I guess Doctor Oswald thought it was for the best. She's not in any pain now, anyway."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I'm sorry to hear that. Listen, it sounds like you need to get out of here. Come along with me, make yourself a new life somewhere else." linkto "JoinDead"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry, Connor. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "JoinRefuseIll"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I'd like to come. I really would, but my mother needs me at the moment. You can understand that, right?"
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You're a good son. Maybe some other time, then." linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just asking. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "JoinDead"
notes "option 1 adds Connor to the party."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "There's nothing here for me now. Yeah. I'll... I'll come with you."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Let's go, then." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "JoinCured"
notes "Option 1 adds Connor to party."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "My mother's alive, and it's all thanks to you. Yeah, I'll come with you. You won't regret this, I promise."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Great. Let's go." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Lifestory1"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "Well... my name's Connor. It's good to meet you, I guess. [He shakes your hand tentatively.] We don't get many as healthy as you around here."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "You look healthy enough." linkto "LifeStory2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Good to meet you. See you around." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "LifeStory2"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "It's only a matter of time, believe me. Everyone who lives here knows they're on borrowed time, before the radiation gets them."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, why are you here, then? Better for you to get out while you can." linkto "LifeStory3"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Yeah - I'm leaving as soon as I can. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "LifeStory3"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "I... I came here with my mother. We lived some distance east of here. A few years ago, she developed symptoms of radiation poisoning. Wasn't a particularly high-rad area - just one of those things."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Go on." linkto "LifeStory4"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I've heard all I want to. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "LifeStory4"
notes ""
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "People in our town were pretty ignorant. Thought that she'd spread what she had to the rest of the folks there. They raised a mob, and gave us the choice of being lynched or leaving. I... I'm not a strong man, I couldn't stand up to them, so we left."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sounds like the only thing you could have done. So you and your mother ended up here?" linkto "LifeStory5"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I wouldn't have let a bunch of trash run me out of my home. I've heard enough." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "LifeStory5"
notes "1) Needs to link to a procedure that check's Fran's health and links appropriately to FranIll, FranDead or FranCured. Asking after Fran also turns 'friend status' with Connor on, so life story doesn't have to be trawled through to ask him to join."
is_wtg = true
{
NPCText "Yeah. Mother worked here for a while scavenging - so did I, and I got pretty good at it. But over the last couple of months, she got really sick, and I had to stop working to take care of her."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "How is your mother?" linkto "FranIll"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry to hear that. Goodbye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Stoopid"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[He smiles sadly.] I suppose some folks have it worse than me. My name is Connor."
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Hello Connor!" linkto "Stoopid2"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Bye bye." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Stoopid2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I'm sorry I can't talk right now. My mother is very sick. Do you know what that means?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Me were sick once. It had carrots in." linkto "Stoopid3"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Bye!" linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "Stoopid3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Yes, that's right. And I have to think of a way to make her feel better. So, go and play somewhere else, please?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay. Me sorry about mother." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
          }
}
Node "Stoopid3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Yes, that's right. And I have to think of a way to make her feel better. So, go and play somewhere else, please?"
      options {
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Okay. Me sorry about mother." linkto "done"  notes ""
